snippet.textDisplay: When Christina and Alex were talking about chef whites in Ratatouille, all I could think about was the ranking system at a restaurant I worked in. For the first 6months I wore long sleeve whites, purely because my bosses wanted to see how clean you worked. And there was a whole ranking system based on colours. If you lasted beyond 6 months, you got short sleeve whites. Beyond 18 months you got short sleeve light greys. Jr sous and sous chef got short sleeve charcoal and Chef got short sleeve blacks.
snippet.textOriginal: When Christina and Alex were talking about chef whites in Ratatouille, all I could think about was the ranking system at a restaurant I worked in. For the first 6months I wore long sleeve whites, purely because my bosses wanted to see how clean you worked. And there was a whole ranking system based on colours. If you lasted beyond 6 months, you got short sleeve whites. Beyond 18 months you got short sleeve light greys. Jr sous and sous chef got short sleeve charcoal and Chef got short sleeve blacks.
